title: Adobe PhotoShop CS2-ME
description:
Adobe PhotoShop CS2 ME "Middle Eastern" does everything English PhotoShop CS can do, plus Arabic-Farsi-Hebrew.

Adobe &#039;PhotoShop CS2-ME&#039; offers exceptional Graphic support for Arabic, Farsi, Hebrew (and other languages). This package also includes a free copy of Adobe ImageReady CS2-ME, ideal for creating web-based graphics -including animated GIF files in Middle Eastern languages.
